    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.poster.avif?t=1752956637\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.webm?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/f8fbb0014ed3decf30a00ea6215d2c5b.mp4?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Concept:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simulation of running and expanding a drive-thru shop where players take orders, prepare various beverages and foods, manage supplies, and serve customers efficiently. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay Elements: <br><br>1. Order Taking: <br>- Receive and input customer orders for both beverages and foods.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.poster.avif?t=1752956637\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/54ca894ced5c59c50004b72737dcce81.webm?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>2. Preparation:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose the correct cup size and shape for beverages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Prepare food items as requested.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.poster.avif?t=1752956637\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.webm?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/b330effcdcd442573463dc8ff4c320c3.mp4?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br>3. Customization: <br>- Customize your shop and prices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.poster.avif?t=1752956637\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.webm?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/ba9b94b096ddfc86b5c743f938082364.mp4?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Payment System: <br>- Process payments using cash, credit cards, or mobile payments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Input amounts, provide correct change, and complete transactions accurately.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 5. Supply Management: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Monitor inventory and restock supplies to keep the shop well-stocked.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.poster.avif?t=1752956637\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.webm?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192740/extras/3ab2e34c892851f07ec733d970c0fa2c.mp4?t=1752956637\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6. Growth and Expansion: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   - Improve and expand the shop by upgrading equipment, adding new menu items, and opening new locations. <br>- Invest profits wisely to enhance the shop's reputation and attract more customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Objective: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Efficiently manage and grow the drive-thru, accurately fulfill orders, maintain adequate supplies, and build a positive reputation for your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers a dynamic and realistic experience of operating and expanding a drive-thru, managing a wide range of beverages and foods, handling diverse payment transactions, and ensuring a steady supply of goods.</p>",
